=====================================================================
CONTACTS
=====================================================================

Echo – Free Spirit of Man – Connection 4, Loyalty 4
Once bound; Olusthra freed it. Now it watches over her, bound by gratitude. It owes her its freedom. It will not let her be taken. Astrally shadowed the ACHE infiltration, unobserved.

Talisen – Elf Artificer – Connection 4, Loyalty 3
Taught her to craft. Knows what she's trying to build. Worries about her obsession. Can appraise the Beta-9 shard.

Rook – Human Fixer – Connection 3, Loyalty 4
She saved his life during a run gone wrong. He finds her work that doesn't compromise her—and takes a smaller cut. Can move the bribe ledgers.

Hiro – Maintenance Contact – Connection 2, Loyalty 2 (NEW)
Met through Matthis. Got Olusthra into ACHE sublevel 12. Impressed by her clean exfil; offered future runs via Rook. [LOYALTY+1]

