ACTIVE THREADS
=====================================================================

[THREAD: THE ORPHAN'S SONG]
Lia (Elena) is a keystone personality holding fragments: Elena (original, sleeping), the Singer (protector, calling for help), and a dark program (weapon trigger). Astral vision revealed this. Activation phrases acquired from ACHE: "Xipil calli tlanextli," "Teyollia in cemanahuac," "Miquiztli xochitl." Trace leads to Aztech black site, Puget Sound Islets, Tacoma. The Singer is approaching merger with Lia—timer accelerates.

[THREAD: ACHE Infiltration] – [RESOLVED]
Infiltrated with Hiro. Retrieved data and Beta-9 shard. Clean exfil, but theft will trigger internal audit within 24 hours.

[THREAD: THE BETA-9 SHARD] – [NEW]
Unstable AI prototype, voice-locked, Renraku-warded. May connect to the dark program within Elena. Talisen can analyze.

[THREAD: AZTECH BLACK SITE]
Coordinates acquired: Puget Sound Islets, Tacoma. Elena was extracted there. Next infiltration target.

