PATCH NOTES ARCHIVE
=====================================================================

SESSION 0: Character created. Olusthra, called by Raven, steps into the sprawl.

SESSION 1 (PART 1): Met Matthis. Learned Elena's history. Astral vision revealed three facets. Trace to ACHE. Arranged meeting with Hiro at East Maintenance Gate.

SESSION 1 (PART 2 – ACHE SHADOWS): Infiltrated ACHE sublevel 12. Used Analyze Device to uncover EV-17 extracted to Aztech black site (Puget Sound Islets). Secured paydata (bribe ledgers, 12k¥). Tapped Beta-9 AI prototype feeds. Conned techs for reset code; stole neural engram core. Exfiltrated clean. Hiro impressed.

