--- RESUME GAME HERE ---
=====================================================================

Rain hammers the alley outside East Maintenance Gate. Your comm buzzes—Matthis: "You in? Talk to me." The datachip burns hot in your pocket, holding Elena's location. The Beta-9 shard hums faintly against your skin—unstable, watching, waiting.

Seattle waits. Raven watches. Echo watches them both.

What do you do?
